launcher.title: Log in
launcher.description: You can log in to the server, log out, set or change your password.

infohub_login_contact.WRITE_YOUR_HUMAN_NAME_OR_THE_SERVER_NODE: Write your human name or the server node name here
infohub_login_contact.WRITE_ANYTHING_YOU_WANT_TO_STORE_WITH_YO: Write anything you want to store with your contact information
infohub_login_contact.THE_DOMAIN_ADDRESS_TO_YOUR_SERVER_KEY: The domain address to your server
infohub_login_contact.THIS_IS_YOU_ON_THE_SERVER_KEY: This is you on the server
infohub_login_contact.YOU_SHARE_THIS_SECRET_WITH_THE_SERVER_KE: You share this secret with the server
infohub_login_contact.CHECKSUM_OF_DOMAIN_ADDRESS_+_USER_NAME_+: Checksum of domain address + user name + shared secret.
infohub_login_contact.YOU_GET_ACCESS_TO_DIFFERENT_APPLICATIONS: You get access to different applications depending on the roles your contact information has

infohub_login_export.HERE_YOU_CAN_EXPORT_YOUR_CONTACT_INFORMA: Here you can export your contact information to a new file
infohub_login_export.USEFUL_IF_YOU_HAVE_SET_A_PASSWORD_ON_YOU: Useful if you have set a password on your contact information file

infohub_login_forget.LET_THE_BROWSER_FORGET_YOUR_CONTACT_INFO: Let the browser forget your contact information on public machines.
infohub_login_forget.YOU_CAN_ALWAYS_IMPORT_YOUR_CONTACT_INFOR: You can always import your contact information file again.

infohub_login_import.IMPORT_YOUR_CONTACT_INFORMATION_FROM_FIL: Import your contact information from file

infohub_login_login.HERE_YOU_CAN_USE_THE_CONTACT_INFORMATION: Here you can use the contact information you imported and login to the server
infohub_login_login.IF_YOU_HAVE_SET_A_PASSWORD_TO_DECODE_THE: If you have set a password to decode the shared secret then enter it here
infohub_login_login.THE_ANSWER_FROM_THE_SERVER_TOOK_TOO_LONG: The answer from the server took too long time.
infohub_login_login.I_WILL_ABANDON_THE_LOGIN_ATTEMPT_KEY: I will abandon the login attempt
infohub_login_login.THE_RANDOM_CODE_DO_NOT_HAVE_THE_CORRECT_: The random code do not have the correct length
infohub_login_login.UNLIKELY_THAT_THE_TOTAL_AVERAGE_HAS_NO_D: Unlikely that the total average has no decimals
infohub_login_login.UNLIKELY_THAT_THE_AVERAGE_IS_EQUAL_TO_TH: Unlikely that the average is equal to the total average
infohub_login_login.THESE_SIMPLE_TESTS_SHOW_THAT_THE_RANDOM_: These simple tests show that the random code at least is not a flat line of numbers.

infohub_login_logout.HERE_YOU_CAN_LOGOUT_FROM_THE_SERVER_KEY: Here you can logout from the server
infohub_login_logout.AFTER_YOU_HAVE_LOGGED_OUT_YOU_WILL_BE_RE: After you have logged out you will be redirected to the login page

infohub_login_password.WHEN_YOU_SET_A_LOCAL_PASSWORD_THEN_YOU_S: When you set a local password then you scramble the shared secret so that it requires your password to work
infohub_login_password.LEAVE_BLANK_IF_YOU_HAVE_NOT_SET_ANY_PASS: Leave blank if you have not set any password
infohub_login_password.YOU_CAN_LEAVE_THIS_BLANK_IF_YOU_WANT_TO_: You can leave this blank if you want to remove the password
